docs/stories/T3-folder-support.md:26:- `GET /folders/:id` returns `200` with the folder and its bookmarks, or `404` when missing.
docs/stories/T3-folder-support.md:27:- `PUT /folders/:id` updates a folder name, returning `200`, or `404` when missing.
docs/stories/T3-folder-support.md:28:- `DELETE /folders/:id` deletes a folder, returns `204`, and nullifies `folder_id` on its bookmarks.
docs/stories/T3-folder-support.md:29:- `POST /bookmarks` and `PUT /bookmarks/:id` accept optional `folder_id`.
docs/stories/T3-folder-support.md:30:- Non-existent or invalid `folder_id` returns `400`.
